        {
            "title": "Burberry銷售額上升 中國市場需求增強",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Burberry銷售額上升 中國市場需求增強\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"639\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RsFtTnbS0G9dpSG2rohteg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/d85bf160-c07b-11f0-afcf-ff7480690147\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Burberry銷售額上升 中國市場需求增強</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
