        {
            "title": "預算案公佈在即 英國第三季度經濟成長幾乎陷入停滯",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xslriagaUDcqTNjxiWmxFQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/55014b464a111c77ca014c4a32318c55\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國經濟成長在第三季度幾乎陷入停滯，此前9月的經濟活動受到捷豹路虎遭遇網絡攻擊，以及對工黨政府即將出台的預算案中可能的增稅措施的擔憂所影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國國家統計局周四表示，第三季度國內生產毛額僅成長0.1%，而第二季度為0.3%。經濟學家和英國央行此前預測成長0.2%。由於服務業的溫和成長被製造業的急劇下滑所抵消，9月單月的經濟就萎縮了0.1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據公佈後，英鎊兌美元一度下跌，但隨著美元整體走軟，跌勢隨即逆轉。英國國債總體保持穩定。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-03302964-8534-3c62-82bd-634932095a85-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R3UVf09juDuxl0Z0Ojkz0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/27d50161735aeac98901683f6839e6b8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在上半年表現優於七國集團(G7)其他所有成員國後，英國經濟成長已恢復到較為平緩的水平。從房地產市場到商業信心調查，越來越多的證據表明，由於擔心財政大臣里夫斯於11月26日的預算會大幅增稅，消費者和企業正在推遲支出決策。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「總體而言，由於稅收增加和海外經濟活動疲軟，英國經濟難以獲得足夠的成長動力，」Capital Economics副首席英國經濟學家Ruth Gregory表示。「而且，即將出台的預算案中的增稅措施可能會使2026年GDP下降約0.2%，因此幾乎沒有理由認為GDP成長會在此基礎上大幅加速。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"691\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UUIw7RfPWHlQlXGP2D5hRg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5e3adfd3b2ab46627520bbaa62181db2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">7月至9月期間，家庭和政府支出僅略有成長，而企業投資連續第二個季度下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：英國首相斯塔默據悉已向遭指責密謀奪權的衛生大臣道歉</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"584\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fUuV.GsxoIpjevnN0NZ8MQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4d7ce5ee9c36272b865178ab425b834a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Economy Barely Grows in Quarter Before Reeves’ Budget (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Mark Evans、Simon Lee、Joel Rinneby.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
